OilField Coiled Tubing Data application made for all specialist who are involved in Oil & Gas exploration and Coiled Tubing Operations. OilField Coiled Tubing Data has most useful informations which are using in daily Coiled Tubing Operations. Also this application is the good supporting tool for Coiled Tubing Engineers.

Application builded by last updated API (American Petroleum Institute) Data.

P.S.: Quick Calculation - Safe Operation Time.

OilField Coiled Tubing Data include:

* Coiled Tubing Dimensions Data;
* Coiled Tubing Stretch Table;
* Nitrogen Calculations;
* Useful Calculations for Coiled Tubing;


Please email us on info@oilfieldengineer.com for clarifications or corrections.

